  "info": {
    "about": "Éclavie is the absolute embodiment of vibrant beauty and timeless radiance—a premium cosmetics house capturing l’éclat de la vie. To match their elite positioning, we architected a cohesive, high-performance digital ecosystem, delivering both a stunning web e-commerce platform and a flawless mobile application tailored exclusively for the luxury market. Our focus was to translate fearless design into an immersive digital boutique. We engineered an intuitive, frictionless user journey where discovering the perfect product feels effortless, guiding customers seamlessly from striking visual inspiration to a secure, premium checkout experience across all devices.",
    "whatWeDid": [
      "· Luxury Brand Strategy & Visual Identity",
      "· UX/UI Design for Web & Mobile App",
      "· Omnichannel E-commerce Development",
      "· Interaction Design & Micro-animations"
    ],
    "technology": [
      "· Next.js / React (Web) · React Native (Mobile)",
      "· Tailwind CSS / Custom Luxury Design System",
      "· CommerceLayer / Headless E-commerce",
      "· DatoCMS · Vercel · Secure Payment APIs"
    ]
  },
